Title : Muharrem Karriqi
Text : {{one source|date=September 2014}}
'''Muharrem Karriqi''' (born in [[Kavajë]]) is a retired [[Albanians|Albanian]] [[Association football|footballer]] who played most of his professional career as playmaker for [[Besa Kavajë]] football club during the 1970s. He is widely considered as the most talented midfielder in club history.<ref>[http://www.panorama.com.al/sport/besa-kualifkimi-i-madh-ne-kohen-e-tollonit-por-kishte-fans-enver-hoxhen/ Besa, kualifkimi i madh në kohën e tollonit, por kishte fans Enver Hoxhën] - Panorama {{sq icon}}</ref>

He won a league title with [[FK Partizani Tirana|Partizani]].

==Honours==
*'''[[Albanian Superliga]]: 1'''
:: [[1978–79 Albanian Superliga|1979]] <ref>[http://www.rsssf.com/players/alba-champ-teams.html Albania - Championship Winning Teams] - RSSSF</ref>

